{
  "id": "adv_main_02_04_03",
  "title": "東京編1章18話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4、1、2、3、4……\n動きがずれてるわ、もっと正確に！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4‚ 1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4…\nYou’re out of sync. Be more precise!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ……\n今の所、もう一回やらせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff*\nPlease let us do that part one more time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "いいわ、全員でもう一度いくわよ\n1、2、3、4……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. One more time‚ all of you.\n1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.80296191771825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 20.6
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 20.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "以前と比べて、動きがかなり良くなりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their dancing has really improved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんの特訓の成果でしょうか\n新しい振り付けも、完成度が高くなっています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to Tendo-san’s instructions‚\ntheir new choreography is achieving higher levels of perfection.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、みなさん\nまだ満足はしてないみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the girls…\nThey still seem dissatisfied.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "スランプを脱出出来た訳じゃなさそうだな\nあと一押しが必要なのかもしれない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess they’re not out of their slump yet.\nThey might need another push.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、天動さんが月ストに\n「最後の特訓」をやってもらうと言っていましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That reminds me‚ Tendo-san did say\nthat she was going to give Moon Tempest their “final test.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 51.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 51.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……ネットの生配信？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A livestream?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ、フェス用に練習している新しい振り付けを\n生配信で初披露するの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. You’re going to broadcast your first performance\nof your new choreography for the festival on livestream.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "泣いても笑ってもチャンスは一度きり\n生放送の一発勝負で成功させる、それが最後の特訓よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For better or worse‚ you only have one chance.\nLivestreaming gives you one shot at success. That is your final test.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達では振り付けをノーミスで成功する確率は\n三割程度ですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ our success rate at executing our choreography flawlessly\nis about thirty percent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それを絶対にミス出来ない緊張感の中で\n成功させろというのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want us to pull off a flawless performance with high stakes\nwhere we absolutely can’t mess up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "どうする？\n自信がないのならやめてもいいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you say?\nIf you’re not confident enough‚ you don’t have to do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、やるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ we’ll do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ここまで全ての特訓をやり遂げてきたのよ\n今更そんなことくらいで怖気づいたりしないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is what all our training was for.\nWe’re not going to let a livestream scare us away now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "なら決まりね。生配信は一週間後\n……失敗したら、罰ゲームがあるから覚悟していてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then it’s decided. The stream is one week from today.\nThere will be a penalty if you fail‚ so brace yourselves for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "罰ゲーム？　なんだろ？\nすずにゃんの卒業アルバムを公開されちゃうとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A penalty? What could it be?\nLike‚ making Suzu-nyan’s graduation album public?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "なんで私ですの！？　……でも問題ないですわ\n私達は必ずやり遂げてみせるのですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why me?! But there’s nothing to worry about.\nWe will succeed with flying colors.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 118.4
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 118.66666666666669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと瑠依さん！\nこの罰ゲームはどういうことですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute‚ Rui-san!\nWhat kind of penalty is this?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、何をそんなに騒いでいるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you all making a fuss?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、これを見て下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! Just look at this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルのみなさんが\n生配信の日時を告知している動画です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE made a video\nadvertising our livestream date and time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "今度の生配信で、もしも月のテンペストが\n振り付けを一カ所でも間違えたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the upcoming livestream‚ if Moon Tempest\nmesses up their choreography by even one step‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.16666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "その時、月のテンペストは\nレボリューションジャムの出場を辞退します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest will withdraw\nfrom Revolution Jam.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達がレボリューションジャムに出演出来るかどうか\nみなさん、注目していて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will they be able to perform at Revolution Jam‚ or won’t they?\nBe sure to tune in and find out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 152.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-ktn006.m4a",
