      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "はい。みんなは私への怒りで心を一つにしています\nその集中力が今の彼女達には必要なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I wanted to unite them in their anger toward me.\nThey need that level of focus right now.",
        "id": ""
