      "startTime": 326.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "なぜ月ストのためにそこまでしてくれるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you doing so much to help Moon Tempest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui024.m4a",
      "text": "……NEXT VENUSグランプリ決勝戦\n大舞台で歌う彼女達を見て、私は全身が震えました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I saw them perform at the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix final‚\nI felt myself tremble all over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 336.96666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui025.m4a",
      "text": "この子達はトリエルにとってライバルだと……\n絶対に負けたくないと思いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized that they were our rivals‚\nand I was determined not to lose to them.",
        "id": ""
