      "startTime": 350.26666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui027.m4a",
      "text": "それはきっと、今の彼女達が完璧を目指し過ぎて\n失敗を恐れ過ぎて……以前の自由さを忘れたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure it’s because they’re aiming for perfection too much.\nIn their fear of failure… they’ve forgotten the carefree feeling they had before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 357.3666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui028.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私が思い出させてあげるんです\nそれは、{user}さんには出来ない仕事です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to help them remember.\nThat’s a job that you can’t do‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 365.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_04_03-rui029.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんは、優し過ぎるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… you’re far too nice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
